*Steps to replicate*
# Create a new page
# Insert Attachments Macro
# Save page
# Upload files (such as PDF or DOC) in the page by 'drag and drop' with the file name:
#* {{6 Six.pdf}}
#* {{7 Seven.pdf}}
#* {{8 Eight.pdf}}
#* {{9 Nine.pdf}}
#* {{10 Ten.pdf}}
#* {{11 Eleven.pdf}}
# Sort the Attachments Macro by File name Ascending

*Observed behaviour*
The attachments list will have the following sequence:
{noformat}
10 Ten.pdf
11 Eleven.pdf
6 Six.pdf
7 Seven.pdf
8 Eight.pdf
9 Nine.pdf
{noformat}

*Expected Behaviour*
The attachments list should have the following sequence:
{noformat}
6 Six.pdf
7 Seven.pdf
8 Eight.pdf
9 Nine.pdf
10 Ten.pdf
11 Eleven.pdf
{noformat}

*Workaround*
Leading zeroes (e.g. 06) can be used to make alphabetical order work correctly. In other words, while 6 is larger than 10 in alpahabetical order, 06 is smaller than 10.

